<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>

<head>

	<title><strong>Grilled Cheese Sandwich</strong></title>
	
</head>

<body>

	<h2><b>Ingredients</b></h1>
	
	<div>

	<ul type="disc">
	    <li>Slice of American Cheese</li>

		  <li>2 Bread Slices</li>

		  <li>1 stick of Butter</li>
	</ul>
	
	</div>
	
	<h2><b>Directions</b></h1>
	
	<div>
		  <p>1. Place 2 tablespoons of butter on a hot skillet to melt.</p>

		  <p>2. Place the 2 slices of bread on the hot skillet once the butter has begun to melt.</p>

		   <p>3. Cook both sides of bread until golden brown.</p>

		  <p>4. Add the slice of cheese to one of the bread slices.</p>

		  <p>5. Place the other slice of bread on top to form a sandwich.</p>

		  <p>6. Heat until cheese melts. </p>

		  <p>7. Ready to eat!</p>
	
	</div>


</body>

</html>
